# AILA Documentation Ignore Patterns
# Generated by: aila document --analyse
# Syntax: Same as .gitignore (https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore)

# === Universal Patterns ===
# Metadata and configuration
**/meta/**
**/.aila/**
**/.kiro/**

# Version control
**/.git/**

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/**
**/venv/**
**/.venv/**

# Build outputs
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.terraform/**

# Python
**/__pycache__/**
**/*.pyc

# === Documentation Files ===
# Don't document documentation
**/KNOW.md
**/SKILL.md
**/META.yaml

# === Test Files ===
**/test_*.py
**/*_test.py
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts

# === Auto-Detected Patterns ===
# Skill provider directories (auto-detected from pyproject.toml)
# None detected

